WEBVTT

00:01.600 --> 00:02.400
You ready for tonight?

00:02.400 --> 00:04.133
bring it on. I got this.

00:04.167 --> 00:05.680
Kind of different in the game.

00:05.680 --> 00:06.601
How different?

00:06.634 --> 00:07.901
Do I even want to ask?

00:07.934 --> 00:10.000
Really, I'm fine.

00:12.701 --> 00:16.545
I told you I wanted to be a mom, and you ran away so fast,

00:16.545 --> 00:18.847
You left an owen-shaped hole in my front door.

00:18.847 --> 00:21.230
You're right, and you didn't deserve that.

00:21.230 --> 00:22.267
I'm sorry.

00:22.300 --> 00:23.734
You're still a jerk.

00:23.767 --> 00:24.901
Hot intern?

00:24.934 --> 00:26.634
- Mouth! - gigi?

00:26.667 --> 00:29.050
The nosy guy across the street

00:29.050 --> 00:30.443
Called and said he saw someone breaking in.

00:30.443 --> 00:32.299
That is peyton's wedding dress.

00:33.050 --> 00:35.601
Someone made an offer for the movie rights to my book.

00:35.601 --> 00:37.400
For "the comet"? that's great!

00:37.400 --> 00:40.801
Not for the "the comet," but, um, "ravens."

00:40.801 --> 00:42.633
You've gotten even more beautiful.

00:42.633 --> 00:43.501
What are you doing here, julian?

00:43.501 --> 00:45.000
Optioning your fiances book.

00:45.000 --> 00:46.334
Like hell you are.

00:46.334 --> 00:47.934
Actually, it's already done.

00:47.934 --> 00:49.868
I see you two have already met, huh?

00:49.868 --> 00:51.334
Yes, we have.

00:51.334 --> 00:53.660
Feels like I've known her for years.

